      <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What if I have a pre-existing condition?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">
        BUPA offers moratorium underwriting (conditions excluded for 24 months, then covered if symptom-free) or Medical History Disregarded (everything covered immediately at higher premiums). Aetna uses full medical underwriting—they review your history and may exclude specific conditions or apply loading.
